\f0\fs64 \cf2 Extracting features from an input is the first step in classification. The input here is the set of files in a project. For source code, we expect an 
\i identifier expansion
\i0  step (e.g., to expand abbreviations) will improve classification. We are implementing algorithms published by others: TRIST (Guerrouj et al, 2012) and GenTest (Lawrie et al., 2006).}

