\f0\fs64 \cf2 After acquiring and setting up server hardware, we created a basic crawling system for GitHub. We generated an index of over 25,000,000 public repositories (e.g., names, descriptions, URLs, etc.), obtained programming language info for 15,000,000 of those, README files for 2,000,000, and finally, downloaded full repository copies for 330,000.}

