\f0\fs64 \cf2 Other groups have explored methods to index software, and text-based source code analysis using machine learning is not new. However, past accuracies have been modest, making the methods unsuited for reliable software cataloging, and the project goals have also been different. Crucially, past work has not explored using semantic knowledge to assist the classification process and organize the results for human use.}

